{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_12", "eventName": "驚霆無聲", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "12-11", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "時不我待", "storyInfo": "變形者集群思考著自己在歷史中存在的意義。凱爾希回顧了自己漫長的一生，將薩卡茲未來的希望寄託在W身上。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "31_g3_mini12_farmland", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_magicchange", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_624_1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_624_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我時常會覺得，時代確實不是均速前進的。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們發明概念的手段如此高明，他們組建社會的方式如此多樣，簡直讓人眼花繚亂。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在卡西米爾生活了很多次，一次次離開，卻又再度回來。不瞞你說，女妖，現在在那片騎士之國中依然有我們的身影。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我必須承認，那裡確實很吸引人。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你沒有讓我為你勾勒出那些霓虹之下的城市。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你只選擇了......把這個普通的村莊作為這次的佈景。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#2$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_624_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為這裡很安靜，我初見卡西米爾時，它就是這個模樣。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "金色的農田與永遠沒有盡頭的原野。可惜，這些對於如今的卡西米爾恐怕已經不再重要。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你看來，這裡和卡茲戴爾相比怎樣？", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾是一片廢墟，但廢墟也意味著其中蘊含著無數的可能性。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然我們對它的想像或許不盡相同，但我們仍可以期待下一座卡茲戴爾。", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_624_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而卡西米爾，它演化得如此之快，眨眼之間，天馬連同他們的道德與榮耀皆已四散凋零。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它卻變得越來越甜蜜，越來越令人神往......", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "神民與先民的後代指責我們薩卡茲吞食他們的血肉，奴役他們的靈魂。於是他們找到了一種新的方式，他們比我們做得更好。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們讓他們治下的人自願被餵食，被吞噬，被化為這頭怪物繼續膨脹生長的養料。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而他們所要付出的，卻僅僅是有關享樂的許諾。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我曾尋找卡西米爾的統治者，他們締造的這一切讓我興致盎然，但我最終發現......", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，這裡沒有統治者，那些公司的發言人，那些商業聯合會的成員，乃至監正會與大騎士長，他們都稱不上是如今卡西米爾的統治者。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "膨脹的欲望足以統治它自己。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_650_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對生存的渴望足以支撐你這樣的索求嗎，變形者？", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#2$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你比我原以為的要更不安，你在害怕什麼？", "name": "Logos"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_650_1#2$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_624_1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在害怕沉淪，沉淪進過去與歷史之中。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是想明白......", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如何與自己相處。", "name": "“卡西米爾人”"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_624_1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g11_wsafehouse", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_openeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔......", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗨，凱爾希，真晦氣，不是嗎？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡......", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不你再睡一下？我還沒來得及往你枕頭下面塞炸彈呢。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我猜，你醒來看到的第一個人是我，一定不怎麼高興。我也一樣。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我寧願去死都不想被誤會成每天流著淚守在你的床前，全心全意等著你睜開眼睛的這一刻。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信我，這是個巧合，我只是來房間裡找水喝的，是你先佔了我的位置。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士和阿米婭在哪？", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得呢？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "搞不好我在你睡死的時候把他們都殺了。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#10$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來他們暫時沒事。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還真是信任我。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們現在的位置是哪裡？", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "倫蒂尼姆城外，我的一間安全屋，現在就連院子裡都塞滿了你的那些可憐盟友。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我的這份恩情在不在你的那些偉大計劃裡，凱爾希？你可以試著發自內心地感謝我，我會考慮接受的。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和阿斯卡綸制定過數種計劃，其中最差的一些情況確實考慮到了借助部分前巴別塔小隊的幫助。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就知道，你會把每個人的用處算計得明明白白——", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我還是要感謝你，W。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如你所說的，發自內心。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......啊？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特雷西斯傷到了你的腦子嗎？我是不是應該把閃靈叫來？", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "凱爾希", "content": "我，"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "凱爾希", "content": "唔——"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會真的去叫閃靈的。傷了腦子對於你未必是件壞事。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#7$1", "focus": "none"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請你......扶我一把。我需要起身。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好吧。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g11_wsafehouse", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_003_kalts_1"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_glassclink", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的水。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_003_kalts_1#4", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#4"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "撤出倫蒂尼姆是一項風險很高的行動，我們現在的處境如何？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你確定要問我？可露希爾正在建那些臨時營房，我們可以在她回來之前，誰也不打擾誰。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我想聽聽你的判斷，雇傭兵對危險的嗅覺更敏銳。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好吧。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#12$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的自救軍盟友們被曼弗雷德耍得很慘。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他和他的小弟看起來終於騰出手來修理你們了，在我看來，這些可憐的市民朋友從來就不是薩卡茲那些刀尖舔血的渣滓的對手。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在這些可憐蟲給趕出倫蒂尼姆了，要我說，這是件好事，總比白白死在巷子裡要厲害。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯一的好消息是大公爵們終於動手了，我收到了伊內絲那女人的情報，博士和小兔子被某一位大公爵拐走打工了，她和他們在一起。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#8$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_003_kalts_1#3", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大公爵......", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#3"}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼說，戰爭還是爆發了。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真遺憾，你錯過了不少刺激的事情。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後悔嗎，凱爾希？你的那些聰明才智似乎沒有換來你想要的結果。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我從未後悔。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "37_i05", "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$dignified_intro", "key": "$dignified_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xTo": 0.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 0.85, "yScaleTo": 0.85, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我偶爾仍會感到......", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......疲憊。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真是難得，你也會露出這樣的表情？我一定要找機會和現在這位可憐兮兮的凱爾希合張影。", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不會自詡為一個試圖躲在陰影裡把握歷史走向的人，雖然有的時候我確實希望事情的發展如我所願。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......和曾經的我採取過很多手段，其中一些獲得了成功，另一些在事後證明仍有可待商榷的地方。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我依然可以斷言，每一個選擇都是基於理性判斷，在當時做出的最佳選擇。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，最佳。", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......“最佳”。這個詞聽起來就像是那些選擇能解決所有問題。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "並非如此，我只能確保事情不向最差的方向發展。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但不論我作何嘗試，最終的結局往往都向我證明，個人的影響終究是有限的。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是誰。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪怕凱爾希這個名字和她承載的記憶已經在這片大地上行走了如此之久，我能做的......可稱得上微不足道。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W，我......曾經的我毀滅過一次卡茲戴爾，那時我相信，這是帶來和平的唯一手段。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們成功斬首了當時的那位魔王，我們幾乎獲得了勝利，按照計劃，魔王的權柄將被回收。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我做好了一切可能性的預案，潛在的魔王繼承者都在我的監控之下。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但特蕾西婭在那一刻......卻選擇拾起了黑色的冠冕。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哼，我對歷史沒有興趣。", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我一直很好奇，凱爾希，你和她為什麼要建立巴別塔？薩卡茲對於你而言到底是什麼？", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你只是想玩弄我們的生命，她......特蕾西婭不會站在你這一邊。", "name": "W"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是發現，薩卡茲們與其他人並沒有我們想像的那麼迥異。既不比任何種族低劣，也不比任何存在高尚。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不論從何處來，我們都已被源石改變成了相似的模樣，擁有了相似的情感與欲望。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如今的這片大地如此醜惡。在薩卡茲眾魂的呢喃裡，他們曾是這個世界的主宰，他們被屠戮，被壓迫，數千年來流離失所。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我曾見過更早的歲月，我曾見過只有薩卡茲行於地上的時代。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事實上，“薩卡茲”這個稱呼的流傳是源於兇手們傲慢的略稱，也成了被傷害者們團結的口號。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "笞心魔與歌利亞的差別如此之大，獨眼巨人與炎魔的外貌如此不同，他們憑什麼同被歸納為“薩卡茲”？", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "若血魔建立起屬於他的國家，這國家與傲慢的維多利亞有何不同？若食腐者統治文明，這文明又與冷酷的烏薩斯有何迥異？", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我與特蕾西婭得出了答案，這些爭端無法通向任何彼岸。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在魔王的回憶中下潛得如此之深，她明白了我一直所憂心的那個可能。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的時間......這片大地的時間，都已經不多了。", "name": "凱爾希"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "37_g11_wsafehouse", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_003_kalts_1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.4}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你為什麼要對我說這些？我已經告訴你了，我對歷史不感興趣。", "name": "W"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_412_1#3$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_003_kalts_1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "正因為你對歷史不感興趣，W。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "歷史使得血魔，巫妖，食腐者，變形者，石翼魔......使得你們成了薩卡茲，卻也使得薩卡茲被這些過往奴役。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "char_003_kalts_1#4", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "卡茲戴爾會被重建，但它會被重建在什麼之上？", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#4"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "W，也許像你這樣的人，會有不同的答案。", "name": "凱爾希"}, "figure_art": "char_003_kalts_1#4"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_towerinside", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還在擔心凱瑟琳嗎，費斯特？", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "傷患們已經暫時安定下來了，那位叫W的薩卡茲雇傭兵......確實很有本事。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自救軍已經在重整編制了，我想，很快我們就能回到倫蒂尼姆了。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#1$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#9$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "洛洛，昨天夜裡，你有看到什麼人嗎？", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你指什麼，薩卡茲的軍隊？", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，當然不是，陌生人，或者......我也不知道。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "到底怎麼了？", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我收到了一封信......今天一早，在我的箱子裡。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是哪位自救軍戰士寫的嗎？", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個筆跡我應該很熟悉，但我確實想不起來......", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信裡說，奶奶在倫蒂尼姆現在很安全，我不需要擔心。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "信裡......還有幾個地址，離這裡不遠。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#8$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "能有這種手段的，只有可能是某位大公爵。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#11$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但大公爵可不是倫蒂尼姆的市民。", "name": "洛洛"}, "figure_art": "avg_4040_rockr_1#7$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別擔心，我很清楚我該和誰站在一起。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論那些大人物怎麼看待我們......我們不是他們的棋子。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#1$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們以為這只是他們爭權奪利的戰爭，他們認為我們沒有資格做出自己的選擇。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自救軍會告訴這些人，他們大錯特錯。", "name": "費斯特"}, "figure_art": "avg_4072_ironmn_1#4$1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}